<HEAD>
   <TITLE>
   The General Conference
   </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="gcback.gif" LINK=#008000 VLINK=#FF0000>

<IMG SRC="gc40head.jpg" ALT="THE IAEA GENERAL CONFERENCE, 40TH REGULAR SESSION" WIDTH=443
HEIGHT=94 ALIGN=bottom>

<H1><FONT COLOR="#008000">Celebrating 40 years of the IAEA</FONT></H1>
<P>
<HR>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=5 WIDTH="600">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=top WIDTH=150>
<P>
<SMALL>
<A HREF="/GC/gc40/documents/agenda.html"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>A</FONT>GENDA</A></B>
 <P>
<A HREF="summaries/"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>S</FONT>UMMARIES AND STATEMENTS</B>
<P>
<A HREF="sciprog/"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>S</FONT>CIENTIFIC PROGRAMME
<P>
<A HREF="pressrel/"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>P</FONT>RESS RELEASES</B>
<P>
<A HREF="/GC/gc40/documents/index.html"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>D</FONT>OCUMENTS</A></B>
<P>
<A HREF="resolutions/1995/index.html"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>R</FONT>ESOLUTIONS ADOPTED IN 1995</A>
AND IN <A HREF="/worldatom/glance/policy/gcresolutions.html">1994</A></B>
<P>
<A HREF="journal/"><B><FONT SIZE=+1>D</FONT>AILY JOURNAL</A></B>
<P>
<A HREF="/worldatom/glance/policy/gcrules.html"><B><FONT SIZE=+2>R</FONT>ULES OF PROCEDURE</A> </B>
</SMALL>
      </TD>
<TD VALIGN=middle WIDTH=20>
<IMG SRC=side2.gif></TD>
<TD VALIGN=top width=380>
<IMG SRC="hilites.gif" ALT=Highlights of the General Conference>
<P>
<B>Stronger development</B> of the Agency's <A HREF="resolutions/1996/gc40dr31.html">safeguards system</A> and
<A HREF="resolutions/1996/gc40dr29.html">technical co-operation programme</A> was endorsed.
<P>
<A HREF="resolutions/1996/"><B>Resolutions</B></A> on the IAEA's verification of nuclear programmes in Iraq and the
Democratic People's Republic of Korea were adopted.
<P>
<A HREF="pressrel/prn2096.html"><B>Eleven new members</B></A> were elected for 2-year terms to the IAEA Board of Governors, 
the 35-member <A HREF="http://www.iaea.or.at/worldatom/glance/policy/">policy-making body</A>.
<P> 
<B>More than <A HREF="summaries/">90 countries spoke</A></B> at this year's Conference during the General Debate.
<P>
<IMG SRC="gcpres.gif" align=left width=50><A HREF="padolin.html"><B>Mr. William G. Padolina</B></A>, Secretary of Science and Technology of the Philippines, served as President of the 40th General Conference.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/blix.gif" align=left width=50><B>IAEA Director General Hans Blix</B> reviewed the Agency's global nuclear programmes. <A HREF="pressrel/prn1896.html">Highlights</A>
or his <A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/dgspeeches/dgsp1996n10.html">full statement</A> are available.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<p>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<P>
