<B><I>WorldAtom</I></B> is the Internet public information and news service of the International Atomic Energy Agency.  It includes <B><I>TecAtom</I></B>, whose pages contain information and databases primarily intended for technical or scientific audiences.  This index groups the information contained in <B><I>WorldAtom's</I></B> main sections, including the customized search tools useful for finding specific information or data.
