<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Programs & Activities
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/program.gif" ALT="IAEA PROGRAMMES & ACTIVITIES">
<BR>
<A HREF="/worldatom/general/latest.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/newbar.gif" WIDTH="76" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" ALT="What's New"></A>
<A HREF="/worldatom/index.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/wabar.gif" WIDTH="76" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" ALT="WorldAtom"></A>
<A HREF="/tecatom.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/tabar.gif" WIDTH="76" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" ALT="TecAtom"></A>
<A HREF="/worldatom/general/iaea-and-internet.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/databar.gif" WIDTH="76" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" ALT="DataLinks"></A>
<A HREF="/worldatom/general/siteindex.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/sitebar.gif" WIDTH="76" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" ALT="Site Index"></A>
<A HREF="/worldatom/general/feedback.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/feedbar.gif" WIDTH=76 HEIGHT=20 BORDER=0></A>
<A HREF="/Architext/AT-mainquery.html"><IMG SRC="/worldatom/images/searchbar.gif" WIDTH="76" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" ALT="Search"></A>
</CENTER>

<HR SIZE="1" NOSHADE>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=10 CELLSPACING=10>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=180>
<I>The Agency's scientific and technical programmes extend to most areas of nuclear energy's 
global development. It operates the world's only international inspectorate in the nuclear 
field -- applying safeguards under agreements in force with nearly 120 countries -- and 
supports nearly 1300 projects to ensure the safe and effective use of nuclear technologies 
in fields of food and agriculture, nuclear power and safety, medicine and health care, and 
industry, science, and the environment.</I>
</TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<dl>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<a href="safeguards/95tables/index.html"><b>Nuclear safeguards & verification</b></a>
<dd><I>Facts & figures</I>
<p>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<a href="safety/"><B>Nuclear safety</B></a>
<dd><I>Updates of services & projects</I>
<p>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<a href="/worldatom/inforesource/annual/anrep95/rwm.html"><B>Radioactive waste management</B></A>
<dd><I>Highlights of studies & programs</I>
<p>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<a href="power/"><B>Nuclear power & fuel cycle facilities</B></a>
<dd><I>Global status reports</I>
<p>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="radapps/"><B>Nuclear & radiation applications</B></A>
<dd><I>Peaceful uses around the world</I>
<p>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<a href="tc/"><B>Technical assistance & cooperation</B></a>
<dd><I>Support for technology transfer</I>
<p>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<B><a href="/worldatom/inforesource/fusion/">Nuclear fusion</A> and International <A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/iter">ITER</A> project</B>
<DD><I>Global cooperation in energy research & development</I>

</dl>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

