<CENTER>
As a leading publisher in the nuclear field, the IAEA issues publications on a range of topics.  This electronic version of the IAEA's
 Publications Catalogue includes  descriptive listings of sales publications issued since 
1980 and covers fourteen major subject areas.  Most publications are issued in English; those 
also available in other languages - Chinese, French, Russian, or Spanish - can be identified 
by the relevant ISBN number in the listings.  Within each category, publications are listed 
in alphabetical order.
