<HEAD>
<TITLE>GC(40)/17 Strengthening the Effectiveness and Improving the Efficiency of the Safeguards System</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=left>
<IMG SRC="http://www.iaea.or.at/worldatom/images/iaeasmall.gif"
