<HEAD>
   <TITLE>
 Unofficial Summations of Statements 
   </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#008000" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/GC/gc40/gc40head.jpg" ALT="40th Regular Session of the IAEA General Conference">
<P>
<I>(Editor's note: These summaries are prepared by the Division of Public Information as a service to delegates and the
 media. They are not official documents and should not be considered or used as such. Full statements are available upon
                              request from the Division of Public Information.) </I>
<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
