<H2>THE IAEA GENERAL CONFERENCE</H2>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=-1><B>40TH REGULAR SESSION, 16-20 SEPTEMBER 1996
<BR>
AUSTRIA CENTER, VIENNA, AUSTRIA</B></FONT>
</CENTER>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
<CENTER>
<H3>General Conference Documents and Resolutions</H3>
<P>
<SMALL><I>Official documents and resolutions of the General
Conference are issued in printed form. Presented here are
selected <B>reports</B> and <A HREF="#information">information
documents</A>, or excerpts from them, related to major items
on the Provisional Agenda.</I></SMALL>
</CENTER>
