<H1>THE IAEA GENERAL CONFERENCE<BR>
<FONT SIZE=-1>
39TH REGULAR SESSION, 18-22 SEPTEMBER 1995<BR>
AUSTRIA CENTER, VIENNA, AUSTRIA
</FONT>
</H1>
<HR SIZE=1 NOSHADE>
<H2>39th General Conference Documents and Resolutions</H2>
<P>
<I>Official documents and resolutions from the 39th General
Conference
are issued in printed form. Presented here are selected
<B>resolutions</B>, <A HREF="#other"><B>other decisions</B></A>,
<A HREF="#info"><B>information documents</B></A> related to major
items on the Provisional Agenda. <A
HREF=/worldatom/glance/policy/gcresolutions.html>Resolutions
adopted during the 38th IAEA General Conference in 1994</A> are
also available.</I>
<P>
</CENTER>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
