<HEAD>
<TITLE>GC Resolutions</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
<H2>Resolutions and Other Decisions of the General Conference</H2>
<B>Thirty-eighth Regular Session
<BR>
19-23 September 1994</B>
<HR size=3>
Governmental delegates from IAEA Member States annually meet to consider matters related to the Agency's
programme, budget and staffing. Selected resolutions and decisions of the latest General Conference can be found here.
</CENTER>
<HR size=3>
<DL>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<B>Resolutions:</B>
<P>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
The Agency's accounts for 1993<I> GC(XXXVIII)/RES/1</I>
