<TITLE>GC Rules of Procedure</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
<H2>Rules of Procedure of the General Conference</H2>
As Amended up to 29 September 1989
</CENTER>
<HR>
<H3>Contents</H3>
<DL>
