<DOCOLDNO>IA029-000313-B040-199</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/GC/gc40/padolin.html 193.81.60.210 19970114120820 text/html 2358
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 1997 12:08:20 GMT
