<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>GNIP Main</TITLE></HEAD><BODY background="t_raindr.gif">
<P><CENTER>
<HR>

<TABLE>
<TR><TH ROWSPAN=2 NOWRAP><IMG height=172 width=180 SRC = "/images/iaeal161.gif">
<TH><H1> <A HREF="http://www.iaea.or.at/">IAEA</A> / <A HREF="http://www.wmo.ch/">WMO</A> </H1></TH>
<TH ROWSPAN=2><IMG SRC = "wmologo.gif">
</TR>
<tr>
<TD ALIGN=center><H2>GNIP -<br>Global Network of Isotopes in Precipitation</H2></TD>
</TABLE>

<HR>
<H3>A Joint Service of the IAEA and World Meteorological Organization</H3>



<P></CENTER>
Welcome to the Global Network of Isotopes in Precipitation (GNIP) and its associated database. 
The IAEA and World Meteorological Organization (WMO) have been surveying the content of hydrogen and oxygen 
isotopes in precipitation since 1961. The data are used for a variety of purposes in fields of hydrology, oceanography 
and hydrometeorology in investigations related to the Earth's water cycle and climate changes, for example.
<P>
Precipitation samples are collected in cooperation with WMO and national meteorological services. 
The samples are analyzed in the IAEA's Isotope Hydrology Laboratory in Vienna, and in <A HREF="lablist.htm">cooperating laboratories</A>. 
Each contributing laboratory is responsible for the accuracy and precision of its own analyses.
Thanks are due to these and other laboratories which have contributed data from private collections. 
GNIP data may be freely used, provided acknoledgement of the source is made.
<HR>

<P><IMG SRC = "/images/blueball.gif"><A HREF="gnipinfo.htm">Description of the GNIP</A>
<P><IMG SRC = "/images/blueball.gif"> Sampling Stations sorted by <A HREF="gnipst_1.htm">Name</A>, <A HREF="gnipst_2.htm">Number</A> or 
<A HREF="gnipst_3.htm">Station no./country list</A>
<H3><A NAME="download">Accessing the Database</A></H3> 
<IMG SRC="exclam.gif"></IMG>The files can be downloaded and are self-extracting. After reception, the file must be executed to decompress.
<P><IMG  SRC="image.gif"></IMG>Geographical Distribution <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/gnipmaps.exe">Map</A> of Stations included in GNIP (Postscript&reg; format).
<P><IMG  SRC="downpage.gif"></IMG> Data in<B> ASCII</B> Format by Region: <b> <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r0ascii.exe">0</A>,   <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r1ascii.exe">1</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r2ascii.exe">2</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r3ascii.exe">3</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r4ascii.exe">4</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r5ascii.exe">5</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r6ascii.exe">6</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r7ascii.exe">7</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r8ascii.exe">8</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r9ascii.exe">9</A></b><BR>
<P><IMG  SRC="downpage.gif"></IMG> Data in<B> Lotus</B>&reg; Format by Region:  <b><A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r0lotus.exe">0</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r1lotus.exe">1</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r2lotus.exe">2</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r3lotus.exe">3</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r4lotus.exe">4</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r5lotus.exe">5</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r6lotus.exe">6</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r7lotus.exe">7</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r8lotus.exe">8</A>,  <A HREF="ftp://ftp.iaea.or.at/pub/gnip/r9lotus.exe">9</A></b><BR>
