<TITLE>AMDIS Introduction</TITLE>
<H1>AMDIS - Atomic and Molecular Data Information System</H1>
<H2>Atomic and Molecular Data for Fusion</H2>
This database service contains atomic, molecular, plasma-material interaction
and material properties data. Both bibliographic and numeric information
is available covering the main processes of interest in thermonuclear energy
research and development.<P>
To try this service as a guest, click 
<A HREF = "telnet://ripcrs01.iaea.or.at">here</A> to start a Telnet session
(username <B>ALADDIN</B>).<P>
To register as a user or to obtain more information, send an e-mail to
<A HREF = mailto:PSM@RIPCRS01.IAEA.OR.AT> 
PSM@RIPCRS01.IAEA.OR.AT</A> giving your name, affiliation, and full mailing
address.
</DOC>
