<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Current Vacancy Notices</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<center>
<font color=#545454>
<b><I>Applications are invited from suitably qualified women as
well as men</I></b></font>
</center>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
<center>
<STRONG>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Current Vacancy Notices</FONT>
<P>
<SMALL>
<A HREF="#adgf">Department of Administration</A> | 
<A HREF="#energy">Department of Nuclear Energy</A> | 
<A HREF="#safety">Department of Nuclear Safety</A> | 
<A HREF="#research">Department of Research and Isotopes</A> | 
<A HREF="#safeguards">Department of Safeguards</A> | 
<A HREF="#technical">Department of Technical Co-operation</A>
</SMALL>
</STRONG>
</center>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
<A NAME="adgf">
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<DL> 
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif
align=bottom><STRONG>DEPARTMENT OF ADMINISTRATION</STRONG>
<P>

<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
