<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/worldatom/inforesource/fusion/ 193.81.60.210 19970114124022 text/html 3584
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 1997 12:40:14 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4
Content-type: text/html
