<CENTER>
<H2>Speeches and Statements of the IAEA Director General</H2>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=90%>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN=left VALIGN=center><I><FONT SIZE=+1>P</FONT>ublic
speeches and
official statements of the IAEA Director General are grouped
chronologically
since 1990.  
They include addresses to international meetings and statements
to the IAEA
General Conference, United Nations 
General Assembly, and United Nations Security Council.</I></TD>
<TD ALIGN=right VALIGN=center><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/blix.gif
alt="Hans
Blix"></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
