UNESCO</A>
</DL>
<A NAME=95>
<HR NOSHADE SIZE=1>
<DL>
<DT><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<STRONG>1995</STRONG></A>
<P>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/dgspeeches/dgsp1995n11.html">Statement to 50th Session of the
United Nations</A>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/dgspeeches/dgsp1995n10.html">International Symposium on
Electricity, Health and
the Environment</A>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/dgspeeches/dgsp1995n09.html">Statement to 39th regular session of
IAEA General
Conference</A>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF="/worldatom/inforesource/dgspeeches/dgsp1995n06.html">Statement to the Review and Extension
Conference of
the Parties to the Treaty on the Non-Proliferation of Nuclear
Weapons</A>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
