<H2>IAEA Newsbriefs Information and Disclaimer</H2>
<hr size=3>
<B><I>IAEA Newsbriefs</b></I> is published regularly by the Division 
of Public Information of the International Atomic Energy Agency, P.O. 
Box 100, A-1400 Vienna, Austria. Telephone (43-1) 2060-21270. Facsimile: 
(43-1) 20607. Telex: 112645. E-mail: IAEO@IAEA1.IAEA.OR.AT.
<p>
<B><I>IAEA Newsbriefs</B></I> is published for information purposes 
only and is not an official record. Items may be extracted or reprinted 
provided acknowledgment of the source is made.
