<body><H1>IAEA Newsbriefs</H1>

<I> Volume 9, Number 3 (65)  JULY/AUGUST 1994 </I>
<HR>
<H2>Contents:</H2>
<DL>
<DD><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/triblue.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF = "#A1.1">38TH IAEA General Conference to Convene in Vienna</A>
<P>
<dl>
<dd><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF = "#A1.2">At its meetings from 6-10 June 1994</A>
<dd><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF = "#A1.3">Safeguards-related matters</A>
<dd><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF = "#A1.4">Technical assistance and co-operation</A>
<dd><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF = "#A1.5">Nuclear safety and radiological protection</A>
<dd><IMG SRC=/worldatom/images/trired.gif align=bottom>
<A HREF = "#A1.6">Programme and budget for 1995</A>
