<DOCNO>WT19-B36-131</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA028-000307-B038-27</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/worldatom/inforesource/bulletin/bull384/schrief.html 193.81.60.210 19970114141823 text/html 17786
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 1997 14:18:18 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.4
