<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT19-B36-209</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA059-000315-B028-255</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nesihp01.iaea.or.at:80/worldatom/inforesource/annual/anrep95/secmat.html 193.81.60.210 19970114150549 text/html 2365
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
